        "text": "|  |  |  |  |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| **Silver Items** | **Hardness** | **HP** | **BT** |\n| **Thin Items** |  |\n| Low-grade | 3 | 12 | 6 |\n| Standard-grade | 5 | 20 | 10 |\n| High-grade | 8 | 32 | 16 |\n| **Items** |  |\n| Low-grade | 5 | 20 | 10 |\n| Standard-grade | 7 | 28 | 14 |\n| High-grade | 10 | 40 | 20 |\n| **Structure** |  |\n| Low-grade | 10 | 40 | 20 |\n| Standard-grade | 14 | 56 | 28 |\n| High-grade | 20 | 80 | 40 |\n\n  \n*Rules for Special Materials*",
